luxury liner is a 1948 romantic musical comedy film made by mgm in technicolor . it was directed by richard whorf , and written by richard connell , karl &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and gladys lehman . it was originally titled maiden voyage . an earlier film with the same title luxury liner ( 1933 ) , starred george brent and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; johann , and was directed by lothar mendes .